<i> I answered his phone.</i>

26:51.911 --> 26:53.177
- [Dr. Deluce]<i> You talked</i>
<i> to his parents?</i>

26:53.179 --> 26:54.345
- Hello?

26:54.346 --> 26:55.512
[Sybil]<i> They'd never</i>
<i> left the country.</i>

