27:00.519 --> 27:01.919
- [Dr. Deluce]<i> How did</i>
<i> you respond?</i>

27:01.921 --> 27:03.320
- [Sybil]<i> I was upset.</i>

27:03.322 --> 27:05.155
[unintelligible arguing]

