<i> And demanded</i>
<i> that he introduce me,</i>

27:06.826 --> 27:09.126
<i> that we were gonna have</i>
<i> a child, their grandchild.</i>

27:09.128 --> 27:11.362
[unintelligible arguing]

27:13.466 --> 27:18.335
<i> After our argument</i>
<i> David apologized.</i>

27:21.007 --> 27:23.440
<i> Said that he just wanted</i>
<i> to keep me to himself</i>

27:23.442 --> 27:25.476
<i> as long as possible.</i>

27:25.478 --> 27:27.578
<i> That he was afraid of</i>
<i> what I would think of him</i>

27:27.580 --> 27:30.080
<i> after I saw</i>
<i> where he came from,</i>

27:30.082 --> 27:31.949
<i> his family.</i>

27:33.953 --> 27:35.819
<i> Should have been</i>
<i> a red flag.</i>

27:36.822 --> 27:38.222
<i> But you let things</i>
<i> like that slide</i>

27:38.224 --> 27:40.924
<i> when you're afraid of losing</i>
<i> something you love.</i>

27:44.163 --> 27:46.430
<i> I insisted</i>
<i> that he introduce me.</i>

27:46.432 --> 27:49.266
<i> Tell me he'd drive to his</i>
<i> parents' house together.</i>

27:49.268 --> 27:51.268
