28:00.446 --> 28:03.480
<i> We were gonna tell them</i>
<i> that we were getting married.</i>

28:04.917 --> 28:07.317
<i> And, like it or not,</i>
<i> for the first time in my life</i>

28:07.319 --> 28:09.620
<i> I was gonna have a family.</i>

