28:19.432 --> 28:21.131
- Hello.

28:22.101 --> 28:23.067
Hi.

28:23.069 --> 28:24.535
- This is, uh,
this is Sybil.

28:24.537 --> 28:26.070
[laughs]

28:26.072 --> 28:28.539
- Nice to meet you.
- How are you, dear?

28:28.541 --> 28:29.573
- Good.

28:29.575 --> 28:31.208
- Hello, Father.

28:33.079 --> 28:35.279
- Sybil, my dear.
[chuckles]

28:36.348 --> 28:38.515
[Rose Holyfield laughs]

28:40.152 --> 28:42.886
You have made my son
a new man.

28:43.422 --> 28:45.022
And I can see why.
- [Rose] Yes.

28:45.024 --> 28:47.157
- You have a rare and
beautiful light in your eye.

28:47.159 --> 28:49.026
- Oh, just gorgeous.
- Just beautiful.

28:49.495 --> 28:51.061
And this.

28:51.063 --> 28:52.513
Oh.

28:52.514 --> 28:53.964
- Oh, I'm sorry.
It's okay.

28:53.966 --> 28:55.432
It's just active today.

28:55.434 --> 28:57.201
[Rose Holyfield laughs]

28:57.203 --> 29:00.070
- You have made us
so very happy, my child.

29:00.072 --> 29:02.272
So very, very happy.
- [Rose Holyfield laughs]

29:03.109 --> 29:04.341
- But I'm rambling.

29:04.343 --> 29:06.343
Let's get this
poor girl inside.

29:07.480 --> 29:09.313
- [Rose] How was the drive?

29:09.315 --> 29:11.448
- [Sybil] Oh, it was lovely...

29:13.953 --> 29:15.986
[whimsical music]

29:15.988 --> 29:18.322
