29:23.496 --> 29:26.130
[speaking indistinctly]

29:28.234 --> 29:31.301
[family chattering
indistinctly]

29:32.371 --> 29:34.638
- The Creek Indians,
before the...

29:34.640 --> 29:36.440
I'm getting my Indians
mixed up here.

29:36.442 --> 29:39.176
The Creek are before
the Cherokees moved in.

29:39.178 --> 29:41.245
They wanted to hunt here
to take it over.
- I'm sorry.

29:41.247 --> 29:42.312
- No, it's fine.

29:42.314 --> 29:43.947
- The fighting was brutal.

29:43.949 --> 29:47.217
The rivers were said
to have, literally, run red.

29:48.420 --> 29:50.721
To this day they call
it Slaughter Gap

29:50.723 --> 29:52.723
and Blood Mountain
overlooks it.

29:52.725 --> 29:56.527
Our family were some of
the early English settlers.

29:56.529 --> 29:58.695
Always vying for position with
the Spanish and then the French

29:58.697 --> 30:04.101
but we kept our ground
and then we found gold.

30:04.103 --> 30:05.435
- Gold?

30:05.437 --> 30:07.371
- The mines are still here
right underneath us.

30:07.373 --> 30:09.640
- But, uh, what about
the Cherokee?

30:09.642 --> 30:12.309
- Well, they didn't
do so well.

30:12.311 --> 30:15.145
- Oh, the Trail of Tears,
I guess.

30:15.147 --> 30:17.381
- And that's enough of
the history lesson today.

30:17.383 --> 30:20.217
Sybil, please, tell me
about your pregnancy.

30:20.219 --> 30:21.585
How are you feeling?

30:21.587 --> 30:23.620
- Hot.
Some morning sickness,

30:23.622 --> 30:26.323
fainting spells
but nothing really--
- Wait.

30:26.325 --> 30:28.025
Fainting spells?

30:28.027 --> 30:30.027
- I mean, I guess
you could call them that.

30:30.029 --> 30:33.297
Blackouts, really,
but nothing serious.

30:33.299 --> 30:34.598
I just...

30:34.600 --> 30:37.067
need to pace myself
sometimes.

30:38.504 --> 30:40.270
Whoo.
- Are you okay?

30:40.272 --> 30:44.241
- Hmm, yeah, it's just
really moving around.

30:44.243 --> 30:46.410
Restless, I think.

30:47.279 --> 30:48.745
- She is special.

30:48.747 --> 30:50.380
You can tell.

30:52.017 --> 30:54.117
- I'm really not.

30:54.286 --> 30:57.054
- You have a gift,
my dear.

30:59.758 --> 31:01.792
[David sighs]

31:05.331 --> 31:06.797
- I told them.

31:08.567 --> 31:11.668
- Not sure that I understand--
- I told them about you.

31:11.670 --> 31:13.737
I told them about...
about...

31:15.040 --> 31:16.406
about you.

31:16.407 --> 31:17.773
- What did you tell them
about me, David?

31:17.776 --> 31:19.176
- I asked you
to be delicate.

31:19.178 --> 31:20.644
[David and Rose arguing]
- I was delicate.

31:20.646 --> 31:22.279
- It's the only thing I said

31:22.281 --> 31:23.480
but you're making her
uncomfortable.

31:23.482 --> 31:24.965
- No, I'm not.

31:24.966 --> 31:26.449
- Nothing to be ashamed of.
- Father, please,

31:26.452 --> 31:27.584
I don't want you to...

31:27.586 --> 31:29.620
- You don't want to what,
David?!

31:36.629 --> 31:39.196
Then why did you
come here at all, hmm?

31:45.638 --> 31:47.237
- It's okay.

31:47.373 --> 31:48.505
- No, Sybil.
- It's okay.

31:48.507 --> 31:51.174
I'm glad that you told them.
- You don't understand.

31:51.176 --> 31:52.709
- Really, it's fine.

31:53.646 --> 31:55.112
This is...

31:55.114 --> 31:56.713
This is awkward.

32:00.552 --> 32:02.552
I'm glad you told them,
David.

32:02.554 --> 32:05.222
Because we're gonna
be a family
- Mm-hmm.

32:05.224 --> 32:07.624
- and I don't want
any secrets.

32:08.761 --> 32:12.829
And I also don't want you
to think that I'm crazy

32:12.831 --> 32:15.432
or be frightened by me.

32:15.434 --> 32:17.701
- [Rose Holyfield laughs]
- Us? Frightened by you?

32:17.703 --> 32:19.603
- [Rose] Of course not.

32:19.605 --> 32:22.639
- But, may I ask,
are you sure?

32:22.641 --> 32:25.409
- Oh, God. Please.
- Are you sure it's real?

32:26.245 --> 32:28.478
- Yes, I'm sure.

32:29.548 --> 32:32.582
- Wonderful.
- Just incredible.

32:33.485 --> 32:35.819
- And can you...

32:35.821 --> 32:38.155
Can you see what
we're all thinking now?
- Stop.

32:38.157 --> 32:39.589
You don't have to answer
this question.

32:39.591 --> 32:41.291
- Are you hearing
something right now?

32:41.293 --> 32:43.727
- Don't make her
feel uncomfortable.

32:43.729 --> 32:45.462
No.

32:45.464 --> 32:47.731
- No, actually.

32:48.300 --> 32:49.766
You know...

32:49.768 --> 32:52.269
I can't read David either.

32:52.271 --> 32:54.421
That...

32:54.422 --> 32:56.572
Sometimes I wonder if it's
connected to a person's

32:56.575 --> 32:59.843
chemical make-up somehow,
like, maybe their genes.

32:59.845 --> 33:02.212
I mean,
I know how to use it.

33:02.214 --> 33:04.281
And I know it works
but that is not to say

33:04.283 --> 33:08.719
that I completely understand
exactly how it works.

33:08.721 --> 33:11.655
- Well, I think it's
fascinating, dear.

33:11.657 --> 33:13.690
And you needn't be
ashamed of it,

33:13.692 --> 33:15.559
at least not with us.

33:15.561 --> 33:18.261
It makes you, you.

33:19.164 --> 33:20.664
- Your parents are great.

33:20.666 --> 33:22.566
[all laugh]

33:24.336 --> 33:26.470
David was so nervous
to take me here.

33:26.472 --> 33:28.372
I have no idea why.

33:28.374 --> 33:30.507
[Rose and William laughing]
- Oh, goodness. Me either.

33:32.378 --> 33:34.611
- I can't believe that
you guys are-- are,

33:34.613 --> 33:35.879
are so wonderful.

33:35.881 --> 33:37.714
It's amazing.

33:37.716 --> 33:39.783
- [Rose] We're just glad
you're here.

33:39.785 --> 33:42.252
- You have to wonder if more
people were able to see

33:42.254 --> 33:43.820
what you see,

33:43.822 --> 33:47.190
it would make the thing
so much easier to understand.

33:47.192 --> 33:49.760
Stronger communications.
Deeper ties.

33:49.762 --> 33:51.495
It would change everything.

33:52.531 --> 33:55.298
- [Rose] What about the dangers
of such a power.

33:58.237 --> 34:00.604
- I don't want to do this.
- Let's not make a scene,
David.

34:00.606 --> 34:01.939
- I don't wanna do this.

34:01.940 --> 34:03.273
I mean it,
I don't wanna do this.

34:03.274 --> 34:04.607
- It was a mistake.
- David, just relax,
it's no big deal.

34:04.608 --> 34:05.941
We made a mistake coming here.
I made a mistake...

34:05.944 --> 34:07.878
- Darling, what are
you talking about?

34:07.880 --> 34:11.615
- We are so fortunate...
- Just have a glass of wine.

34:11.617 --> 34:15.852
[indistinct conversation]

34:16.755 --> 34:17.821
Calm down.

34:17.823 --> 34:20.390
[distorted voices]

34:20.392 --> 34:21.925
- ...Your ability, Sybil.

34:21.927 --> 34:24.961
[indistinct conversation]

34:26.598 --> 34:28.298
- Sybil?

34:38.644 --> 34:40.077
What's wrong?

34:40.078 --> 34:41.511
- Somethings wrong.
- What have you done to her?

34:41.513 --> 34:42.712
Sybil?

