what you did to me?

1:21:04.493 --> 1:21:06.160
- Yes.

1:21:10.766 --> 1:21:13.167
- They still have my baby.

1:21:29.719 --> 1:21:32.319
You know,
it's incredible, really,

1:21:33.623 --> 1:21:36.590
I loved you more than
I thought was possible.

1:21:38.294 --> 1:21:40.361
