when I was a child.

1:22:14.664 --> 1:22:18.565
That's why they paired us
so our baby would be pure.

1:22:18.567 --> 1:22:21.302
But I'm not one of them,
I'm the same as you.

1:22:22.138 --> 1:22:24.271
I'm not their son.

1:22:24.273 --> 1:22:26.607
I'm property,
I'm a slave.

1:22:28.277 --> 1:22:29.677
